'''Giant bats''' are [[monster]]s commonly found within caves and dungeons. They drop [[bat bones]], which provide slightly higher [[prayer]] experience when buried in comparison to regular [[bones]], and are also used in a few quests.

==Locations==
*[[Crandor and Karamja dungeon]]
*[[Gnome Village dungeon]]
*[[Taverley dungeon]]
*[[Waterfall dungeon]]
*[[Yanille agility dungeon]]
*South of [[Seer's Village]]
*[[Legends' Guild]] dungeon

